WEBVTT

00:00:48.280 --> 00:00:49.480
Okumino En. Tag.

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:52.840
Thread the needle through the hem,
starting 5 millimetres from the edge.

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:59.840
From 4 centimetres above the hemline to 5
centimetres above the

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:01.520
collar depth measurement.

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:05.000
Make a triple-fold stitch
at 1-centimetre intervals.
